creator: Realist
descriptionHtml:
Green-Acres is the leading real estate portal for the purchase of secondary houses in Europe.

With more than 400,000 listings, in 22 countries, we are the reference platform for buyers looking for a second home in Europe.

More than 9,000 real estate agents and individuals put their properties for sale throughout Europe on Green-Acres and in English!

Whether you are looking for a villa in the Algarve, a farmhouse in the south-west of France, a house in Florence, an apartment in Malaga, a property in Athens or even Tel Aviv, you have come to the right place!
